(112, 1, '2014-05-12 13:32:40', '2014-05-12 11:32:40', '<h2 style="font-weight: 500;"><a style="color: #222222;" title="A well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd." href="http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website_agri/htdocs/a-well-known-south-african-institutional-investor-invests-r78-million-in-acorn-agri-pty-ltd/" rel="bookmark">A well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd.</a></h2>\n<p class="byline vcard" style="font-style: italic; color: #9fa6b4;">Posted <time class="updated" datetime="2014-04-2">April 2, 2014</time> by <span class="author">Investment Team</span></p>\n\n</section><footer class="article-footer"></footer>\n\n<hr />\n\nA well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd.\n\nPosted April 2, 2014 by Investment Team\n\nAcorn completes the purchase of a significant stake in Overberg Agri through the newly incorporated Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd in a deal worth approximately R200m.\n\nPosted February 7, 2014 by Investment Team\n\nAcorn Agri (Pty) Ltc is incorporated\n\nPosted February 7, 2014 by Investment Team\n\n', 'News', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-05-12 13:32:40', '2014-05-12 11:32:40', '', 13, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/acorn/13-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2014-04-10 13:25:04', '2014-04-10 13:25:04', '2 April 2014\r\nA well-known South African institutional investor invests R78 million in Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd.\r\n\r\n10 February 2014\r\nAcorn releases a flash update on performance and transactions for the start of 2014 to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n7 February 2014\r\nAcorn completes the purchase of a significant stake in Overberg Agri through the newly incorporated Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd in a deal worth approximately R200m.\r\n\r\n31 January 2014\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n20 January 2014\r\nAcorn completes second exit from General Fund 1. USC is sold to a trade player.\r\n\r\n13 January 2014\r\nAcorn completes first exit from General Fund 1. Target Investment is sold to a trade player.\r\n\r\n31 October 2013\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n31 July 2013\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n30 April 2013\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n31 January 2013\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n27 November 2012\r\nAcorn successfully concluded a transaction between Overberg Agri and Moorreesburgse Koringboere to the value of R927 million.\r\n\r\n31 October 2012\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n31 July 2012\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n30 April 2012\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n31 January 2012\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n31 October 2011\r\nThe quarterly performance update is available to investors and interested parties.\r\n\r\n26 August 2011\r\nAcorn General Fund One is fully invested. This is an achievement the Acorn team is proud of as it was achieved within 21 months of the fund´s first close.', 'News', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-10 13:25:04', '2014-04-10 13:25:04', '', 13, 'http://192.168.1.15/~tyronestafford/acorn/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
